Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.97,0:00:03.51,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,The water is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:10.28,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Once you dive in, it will immediately \Nbare its fangs and attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:14.28,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,But there's nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:16.68,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resist the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.68,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Thrust your fingers into the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.36,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,and carve an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:23.16,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Then you slide your body \Nthrough that opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.25,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Moving your arms, your head, your chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:31.33,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,His swimming always looks so smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:33.22,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, like a dolphin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:36.89,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:38.61,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka Rin-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:41.81,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He transferred into our class last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:17.80,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can beat you when \Nyou're in the water, Haru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:21.90,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me -chan already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:25.96,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That was so cool, Nanase-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:28.69,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna swim like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.57,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You're as fast as the rumors said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.17,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,What was your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:35.61,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:40.20,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like the rumors said, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:43.51,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nanase.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:44.79,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You interested
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.25,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,in entering a relay with me \Nat the next tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:51.25,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I only do freestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:54.88,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I don't care \Nabout swimming faster times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:57.80,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,All I want is to feel the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:01.42,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,With my skin, my eyes, my soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.52,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,To never doubt what it makes me feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.37,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.84,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resist the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:09.05,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.65,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,We accept one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:14.57,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:18.32,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,There was some funky stuff going \Nthrough my head back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.70,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,There's an old saying my \Nlate grandma taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:24.79,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,When you're ten, they \Ncall you a prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.37,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,When you're fifteen, \Nthey call you a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:28.32,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Once you hit twenty, you're \Njust an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.13,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,About three years until I'm ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:36.09,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.31,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to be ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:14.31,EpTitle,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,432)}Reunion at the Starting Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.99,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Tamura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:20.32,Main,Tamu,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Makoto-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.28,Main,Tamu,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.97,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:24.90,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,See ya around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:25.82,Main,Tamu,0000,0000,0000,,Take care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.07,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.34,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:52.64,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.27,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:02.78,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.62,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Haru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.92,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to lay off the -chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.71,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the bath with \Nyour swimsuit on again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.83,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Buzz off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.04,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.71,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.71,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why are you grilling fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:32.00,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.73,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,And you're wearing an \Napron over a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.68,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.89,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get oil on my swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.03,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Toast and fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.15,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.75,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:50.02,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't show up for the \Nopening assembly yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.70,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I called in sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.16,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know which class you're in, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:57.57,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:58.98,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.31,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a new lady as \Nour homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.95,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,They already gave her a nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.24,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,She teaches classical literature,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:08.00,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but she's a little on the odd side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:08.47,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It needs to get warmer so \NI can swim in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:13.07,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it gets warmer \Nsoon so you can swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.71,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Tadokoro Junichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:17.60,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.04,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Tezuka Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:19.86,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.64,Matsuoka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\fs20}Nanase Haruka
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.03,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.58,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nanase Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.78,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to being mistaken for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.56,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, Haruka's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:30.78,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.77,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Nanase-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.37,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,You were absent yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:40.06,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Amakata Miho, your \Nnew homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:40.83,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:44.09,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Miss Ama-chan is from this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.86,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,She went to college in Tokyo \Nand found a job there,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.05,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but she came back after \Nher dream fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.27,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What was her dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.11,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me. Maybe she \Nwanted to go into music?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:54.83,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be \Nlearning from a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:57.08,Nar/Thought/Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,who became a teacher as plan B?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.41,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.18,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,So, lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.31,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna eat on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.15,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,He needs to get a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.13,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,Gou, what are you doing? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.36,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.40,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,And don't call me Gou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.39,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.80,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.66,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Go buy something, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.83,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want some of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:21.83,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.17,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan! Mako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.09,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's been forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.71,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be joining you here \Nat Iwatobi High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:29.93,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Mako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:31.03,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:33.94,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.82,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:40.57,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I saw you after the \Nswimming club was shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:44.52,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, because I went to a different school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.87,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,There are cherry blossom \Ntrees next to the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:50.32,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't there cherry blossom \Ntrees next to the pool
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,at your grade school, Haru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.96,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stop calling me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.55,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,But that's your name, Haru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:00.79,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,But that pool is old and not in use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.24,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,There's no swim club, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.00,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you swim, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.25,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I quit swimming competitively.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:07.99,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:09.45,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you quit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:13.05,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I was all excited about getting to \Nswim with you again in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.48,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,We're not little kids anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.68,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Things aren't the way they used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.40,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.93,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he stopped swimming competitively,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:23.92,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,but he still loves water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.29,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru can't live without being in water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:28.12,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,During the summer, he \Nswims in the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:30.62,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,and he was soaking in \Nthe tub this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.84,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have \Nto do with swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.55,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That just means he likes baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.12,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I know! How about a hot springs club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.89,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start a hot springs club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.46,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.78,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa hasn't changed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.84,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:42.49,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:43.71,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:44.49,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.21,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:50.70,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I should have gotten \Nthe same thing you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.25,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:09:00.35,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,The swimming club we went to in grade \Nschool is gonna be torn down soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:04.35,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,So before that happens, \Nwhy don't we pay a visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.31,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,To dig that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:07.48,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.98,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We can sneak in at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.89,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You can go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.66,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:14.88,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us, Haru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:15.86,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.72,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it'll be fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.70,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.40,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just humor him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.02,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's too much effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.00,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a pool there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:29.01,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,A pool is much bigger than a bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:33.93,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:36.40,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You live by yourself, Haru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:39.68,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,His mom went with his dad when \Nhe had to move because of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.50,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, fish again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.99,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's forcing you to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.25,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.33,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan was always a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.61,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.24,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you all for it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.76,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.99,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:57.75,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for just the \Nthree of us to dig it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.60,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't do anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.53,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan isn't in Japan anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:08.72,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be attending middle school here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.99,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean, Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.63,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.84,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you're going \Nto a different country?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.22,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I'm going to a swimming school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:26.35,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.56,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become an Olympic swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:32.13,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.49,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What about the relay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.05,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll swim in the relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.35,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the day after the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:40.34,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,So this will be the last time \Nthe four of us swim together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.33,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I only swim freestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.33,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have \Nto swim in the relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.20,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,This is our last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.46,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's swim together, Nanase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.21,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,If you swim with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:04.90,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you a sight \Nyou've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:10.44,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,The place is pretty trashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.11,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Here, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.28,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Purifying salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:15.36,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:18.12,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,They say the place is haunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.37,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.08,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:23.45,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,People have been seeing \Nshadows moving around
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.83,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,and hearing sobbing voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.26,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Stand still.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.75,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. You're next, Haru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.40,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.21,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.95,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't salt. It's sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:46.36,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's all mental anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:48.85,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,so sugar will still get the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.22,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Clichéd as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:52.39,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0} one of the oldest mistakes out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:54.73,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.23,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,My foot hit an empty can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.55,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing this on purpose, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.13,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You always were scared of the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.23,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You're not helping any!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.56,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.57,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.50,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as trashed inside as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.25,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.33,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,The lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.46,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.22,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:27.71,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the picture from \Nwhen we won the relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:37.64,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you a sight \Nyou've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:51.46,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,The four of us won this together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.80,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,so it doesn't make sense for \None person to take it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.73,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,So let's put it in a time capsule
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.46,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,and dig it up when we're grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:04.01,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Romantic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:06.43,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.25,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:10.97,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.73,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Think the marker is still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.05,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Can we pick up the pace a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:30.88,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:33.05,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:33.95,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.67,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd run \Ninto you guys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.02,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.02,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.13,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're back from Australia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.67,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.92,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,This must be fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:53.83,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Some unseen force brought \Nus all here at this exact—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:57.06,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, you're still hanging \Nout with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.45,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:01.79,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.57,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.77,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Have you learned anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.45,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.91,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.26,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I show you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:11.45,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's race, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.83,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Race?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:13.99,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:16.05,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did they just ditch us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:17.14,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.50,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:24.01,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how different we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.01,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.55,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.06,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to swim here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:31.93,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.60,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, that's a bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.52,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you've been wearing \Nthat the whole day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:37.39,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.95,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:39.93,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Do we really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:40.52,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.70,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.30,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:49.93,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,go—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.08,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't any water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.54,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.10,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.96,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Did you guys \Ncome here for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:05.59,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, our trophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:09.15,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need this thing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.19,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.58,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.85,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He's kinda changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.15,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.94,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.96,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.62,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan was really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.67,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Look-alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:36.92,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a look-alike \Nchallenge you to a race?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.28,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.49,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.97,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Doppelganger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:42.85,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:46.49,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We used to do that at the swimming \Nclub! Super Fusion: Doppelga—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:47.50,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down, Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.12,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.48,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:51.45,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:54.62,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:55.30,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.98,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't you remember, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.14,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Nanase Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:57.73,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.23,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:15:59.83,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.36,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Hazuki Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.77,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,What they have in common is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.38,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Must be a generation gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:04.07,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,that they used to belong to \Nthe same swimming club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.42,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm only one year older than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.31,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And Haru's the same age as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:07.73,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,And they're all boys with girlish names.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.52,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,What's your relationship with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:11.08,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:14.60,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,That means you have something \Nin common with them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:17.02,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a girl with a boyish name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.87,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. Stop calling me Gou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.62,Faculty,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Faculty Office
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.62,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.21,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The place may be abandoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.62,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but it's still trespassing if \Nyou enter without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:26.75,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.44,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.51,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.18,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Nanase?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.98,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He left early this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.28,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.79,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. I think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.52,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Think back to what Li Bai once said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.44,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,In human life, accomplishment \Nmust bring total joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:48.02,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Do not allow an empty \Ngoblet to face the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.85,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,You only have one life, so \Nyou should do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:56.34,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,It would be foolish not to drink \Nfrom the glass placed before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:57.45,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.33,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.95,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka Rin, Matsuoka Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he really go to our school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.11,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,If he's back from Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:09.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,he might have transferred \Ninto our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.74,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't see him at \Nthe opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:13.80,Matsuoka,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.16,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:14.89,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:16.11,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,No, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.05,Matsuoka,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka Gou
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.05,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka Gou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.57,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.38,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:26.47,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That was Rin's sister, Matsuoka Gou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:44.33,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,So you also chose Iwatobi \NHigh School, Gou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.79,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Gou. Everybody calls me Kou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.68,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:53.42,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Gou, like the Sengoku warlord \NAzai Nagamasa's third daughter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.95,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:58.57,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,But the typical reading \Nis Kou, so call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:00.39,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the nice thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.02,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, putting that stuff aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.44,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}stuff{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:05.02,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.14,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you doing at Haru's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:08.53,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.52,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask him about my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:14.74,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,So Rin is really back from Australia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:19.86,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,He returned last month and he's \Nattending Samezuka Academy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:23.19,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,It's a boarding school, \Nso he hasn't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.37,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Samezuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.30,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,The swimming powerhouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.37,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:31.05,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's visit Samezuka Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:32.58,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to see Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:33.88,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,We saw him yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:39.92,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Here I was thinking you'd finally \Nget to swim if you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:43.60,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Samezuka is supposed to \Nhave an indoor pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.56,samezuka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Samezuka Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.37,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're slowing down, Nakagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.32,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.91,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.29,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.83,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:05.78,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.36,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take your clothes off here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.97,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who brought \Nme here to swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.59,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Haru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.14,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait until practice is \Nover and everyone's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:17.94,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.72,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll still be trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.10,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:25.31,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That teacher earlier told us to \Ndo what we want with our li—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.23,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.07,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I still think this is a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.57,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:41.61,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.87,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan still reminds me of a dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.12,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mako-chan, let's swim with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.35,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no! We'll get in trouble if they find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:54.22,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to look for Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:55.75,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We can take a little dip first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.58,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody will find us if we \Ndon't turn on the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.01,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't bring a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.38,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,A little skinny dip, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.08,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:03.59,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I can swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.28,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mako-chan, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:09.50,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.73,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna join you—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.79,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.66,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like an elephant falling in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:25.17,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:27.09,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:29.62,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.44,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:31.71,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.25,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:42.09,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.17,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:44.81,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We came here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:45.47,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.49,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:53.48,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Free...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:55.01,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.21,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.46,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I only swim freestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.24,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.20,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.57,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,About three years until I'm ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:15.55,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it couldn't hurt \Nto wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.78,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to show me that sight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:23.88,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I've forgotten what it was that I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:29.48,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:33.31,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't be the same this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.89,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be showing you something \Ncompletely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:15.75,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,So is there a reason Nanase-san \Ncan only swim freestyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.47,0:23:19.58,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan doesn't want to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:21.64,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mako-chan, can you answer for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.64,0:23:23.31,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:26.65,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Should I use salt or miso on my fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:28.38,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He's thinking about dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.69,0:23:31.11,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Memories in the Distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:36.02,NextEp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(482,1)}Memories in the Distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:32.76,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,You even did the preview for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.90,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up for some Meuniere sauce.
